<h2>Policy Setting</h2>
[img class="tc-image-documentation" [$:/ipfs/saver/image/settings/policy]]
<p>
  <b>Ipfs with ~TiddlyWiki</b> is able to reach the Ipfs network with multiple providers:
</p>
<ul>
  <li>[ext[Ipfs Companion|https://github.com/ipfs-shipyard/ipfs-companion]]</li>
  <li>[ext[Http Client|https://github.com/ipfs/js-ipfs-http-client]]</li>
</ul>
<p>
  Options:
</p>
<ul>
  <li>
  <b>Default Ipfs Provider</b>
  <ol>
    <li>Try to use <b>Ipfs Companion</b> if available otherwise fallback</li>
    <li>Use the embedded <b>HTTP Client</b> provider</li>
  </ol>
  </li>
  <li><b>Ipfs Companion</b> only uses the <b>Ipfs Companion</b> provider</li>
  <li><b>HTTP Client</b> only uses the embedded <b>HTTP Client</b> provider</li>
</ul>
<p>
  When the [[Verbose]] property is selected, the console always shows which policy is used.
</p>
